thread.title: Carol St Andrew
thread.title_full: MOO.COM reviewed by Carol St Andrew

author: Carol St Andrew
title: Carol St Andrew
text: My cards were shipped via UPS to USPS but the status indicates via UPS that it is at the post office for over 2 days but USPS claims they don't have the package. Customer service reprinted my cards and is sending them faster shipping despite the fact that the guaranteed date of arrival has not passed. Great customer service. I love their product as well. Will order again.
